title: TrendForce anticipates first annual decline in Samsung smartphone shipments
text:
TrendForce anticipates first annual decline in Samsung smartphone shipments 
Published By: AndroidAuthority.com - Today 
Market researcher TrendForce anticipates that Samsung will see its first ever year-over-year decline in handset shipments in 2015....
